						<summary>

						<p>On the back of the slab containing the image of Āñjanēya.</p>						

						<p>Vijayanagara; Dēvarāya.</p>						

						<p>This inscription contains the name of the cyclic year Hēviḷaṁbi.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record the remission of tax as <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> by Vīrayya probably to certain individual.</p>						

						</summary>
